          "id": "marugoto_a1_l2_dialogue_1",
          "type": "dialogue",
          "title": "Dialogue marugoto_a1_2",
          "text": "Conversation: test\nThere: will be five questions. If you can answer three out of five, you will pass.\nすばらし: Excellent! You answered all the questions and were able to have a conversation.\nできました: Well done! You answered three or more questions and were able to have a conversation.\nもうすご: Getting there! You could not understand or answer the questions well.\nSpeak: in groups.\n华: テストのあいだに4にんぐらいの ちいさいグルプになつてつぎの(1)と(2)を\nWhile: waiting to take your test, make small groups of about four people, show (1) and (2) below and talk about\nthem: (1)にほんご・にほんぶんかのたいけんきろく\nRecords: of your experiences of Japanese language and culture\nThings: you wrote in lesson 2: name card, lesson 7: e-mail, and lesson 10: birthday card.\nShare: the things you talked about in groups with other",
          "sourceRef": {
            "sourceId": "marugoto_a1_textbook",
